title: Fox | Pro Circuit
description:
“We Race” has been Pro Circuit’s mantra for the past four decades. For a long time it has felt as if they were alone in that effort. Since the beginning, Fox and Pro Circuit have been establishing legendary legacies in differing ways: The steel that drives us forward, and the fabric that binds us together. Combined we have a total of 98 pro championships. Today we join two different families, a blending of two unique backgrounds with a single focus that will forever change the course of history. Forging a strong bond through effort and persistence;
From this day forward, We Race Together.
